Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:22:59.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
