Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:56.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:24:02.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:05.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
