Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:20.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:51.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
